arts.ttl: Victor Osimhen: Man Utd & PSG make offers for Napoli striker
arts.sum: Man Utd and PSG are both prepared to trigger Victor Osimhen's release clause with Napoli.

Rizespor were beaten 3-2 by Kasimpasa last time out. They could have easily gotten a point but their hosts proved to be better finishers on the day. Abdulkadir Omur could prove to be a great signing ...
